G
G_\alpha = \{g\in G \mid g\cdot \alpha = \alpha\} = Stab_G(\alpha)
G_{S} = \{g \in G \mid S^g = S\} = \{g \in G \mid g\cdot\alpha \in S\; \forall\; \alpha \in S\}
S
G_{(S)} = \bigcap_{\alpha \in S} Stab_G(\alpha) = \{g \in G \mid g\cdot \alpha = \alpha\; \forall \; \alpha \in S\}
G_{(S)} \unlhd G_S
